 
<p>
Murderous drug mafias have led the Netherlands to 
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/jul/03/mob-style-killings-shock-netherlands-into-fighting-descent-into-narco-state">launch a sort of war
on drug mafias.</a>
<p>
I would guess that most of the drugs smuggled through the Netherlands
is headed for other countries in Europe, and only a small fraction is
for Dutch users.  If there were a lawful way to buy cocaine for
personal use, it might pull the rug out from under the mafias.

 